column1: Table 6. mRNA relative abundances in M9 + glucose and LB media
This table contains the relative abundances for individual mRNAs in M9 + glucose
and LB media. Relative abundances were determined by using mRNA harvested from
cultures grown at 30ÂºC to OD600 = 0.8 as described in Materials and Methods.
The data in this file were used as source data for Fig. 3A.
